Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,3004)}So Ra No Wo To
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is how we'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.64,0:02:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.98,0:02:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll begin the mission-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.08,0:02:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading out, Kana-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.84,0:02:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.59,0:02:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's off to use her first paycheck.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.40,0:02:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sending some home, and I wanted\Nto send a present along with it, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little present for yourself, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.46,0:02:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were a trainee for the first month,\Nso you didn't get paid a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.38,0:02:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be nice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd heard that we're usually paid late,\Nand that it's normally in scrip...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I'd get real money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.27,0:03:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we have our other jobs-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.14,0:03:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a market in town today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your first time at one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the perfect time to use your\Nfirst day off and paycheck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.99,0:03:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about work and go enjoy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.73,0:03:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata's Day Off - Hair Braiding
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to tip her off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.88,0:03:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one would believe
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we get paid on time out here,\Nin the middle of nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She believed it, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's part of what makes her Kana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like you two, who immediately wondered\Nwhere the money came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's forget about our main jobs, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's one problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lowering the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, excuse me. I was enjoying myself, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, no problems at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We{\i0} have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've got a suggestion to go with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us the details, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one's cute, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are the sellers, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I take it you like the goods?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my. And what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take lots of work and connections\Nto sell these.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough so that it's not quite\Nworth our time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my policy to give discounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The price is part of the taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's asking you to cut the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're taking it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even think it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead, shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Course, before ya do,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my gun'll blow a hole straight through\Nthat pretty head of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not too swift, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:07:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you get for underestimating us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.86,0:07:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night, children.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I warned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:07:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The car!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about the present for the big boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't do us any good if we're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one told me they were this crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never coming back to this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.16,0:08:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we're done, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.78,0:08:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was scared there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we fooled them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.50,0:08:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we wouldn't stand a chance\Nagainst the central area mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You scratch our backs, we'll scratch yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll be reimbursing us for our parts\Nin this little play, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my. Mikhail-san, you're such a kidder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not kidding at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is business now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.09,0:09:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I pay it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you the ones who crushed their car?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.39,0:09:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone smashed their car up pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.46,0:09:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside were all these spoils of war\Nthey bought at the market.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.88,0:09:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take them
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and give you half the profits.\NHow's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we have a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that play is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you were really into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the military discovered we distilled this,\Nwe'd get a lot more than a court martial.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:09:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a violation of the monopoly\Nand tax laws, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.10,0:10:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And at worst, treason.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We took this job over from\Nthe last group here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio's never opposed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a bit surprised, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at first I was shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I learned my mother's\Nbeloved calvados was made here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it may be your mother who\Nled you to being deployed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina-oneechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.94,0:11:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks wonderful, Seiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-san, it's time for their\Nfirst visit to the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The priest will be there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.34,0:11:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So at least for today-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.26,0:11:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cause problems for her, Mishio!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not do your hair right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.90,0:11:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always tell me to!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't do that, Mishio-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.45,0:11:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10 yen 25 sen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.69,0:12:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey girl, that's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, excuse me. I was enjoying myself, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They seem to have found\Nout about the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.57,0:12:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.73,0:12:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But anyway, Naomi-san! What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never had enough money\Nin my wallet to buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I asked for it, I could buy it, couldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. What if someone came\Nand tried to buy it for themselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone say they wanted it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. It was just an example.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.84,0:12:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd tell them that dolphins are very\Nscary animals that eat people,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:12:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they wouldn't want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.81,0:13:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! You're a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll keep that dolphin
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until you say you don't want it anymore,\Nso think about it in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll buy a present for\Neveryone else first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Dad, Mom, Granny and Grandpa,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then my Grandma and\NGrandpa in Waren,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great-Grannie, and then old\Nlady Nanae next door too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Look at all the stuff they're selling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.45,0:13:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.08,0:13:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She says she's looking for a box.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.89,0:13:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A box?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see one like this anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:13:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to help you look?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.46,0:14:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm buying presents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping there would be
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.07,0:14:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,something wonderful to send\Nto my family back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not in a hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.01,0:14:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't know about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a nice shirt, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Note: Shirt says "Yoroshiku" (greeting)\Nwritten in "gangster/thug" Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.45,0:14:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one's cute, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.46,0:14:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Kanata-san, did you see Mishio-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A box?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. She said it was important.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:15:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.31,0:15:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When her mother died, all her\Nfamily's property was taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A memento of her mother was\None of the items taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time there's a market,\Nshe thinks she might find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have said what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got paid for the first time yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so I told her I was getting\Npresents to send my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... We are her family now, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she's still jealous, that just\Nmeans I'm not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mom? Which is more important,\Nme or your box?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.28,0:16:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.17,0:16:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The famous Treize firecrackers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear them pop?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.28,0:16:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who wants some?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.85,0:16:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina-oneechan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.80,0:17:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The car!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.49,0:17:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I'm not Yumina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina-oneechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.83,0:17:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.66,0:17:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.81,0:17:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, that car... Was it yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's 150 yen in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay you back...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great work, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already gotten my payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.57,0:18:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Naomi-san, that box!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These ideographs mean\N"beautiful rice stalk."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.89,0:18:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carve them into her seal, and she'll live a\Nhappy life, like a full field of rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miho, you're lucky to have received\Nsuch a nice name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find Mishio-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've done everything I can\Nthink of to be her family,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm not good enough yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're doing your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.14,0:19:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.23,0:19:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take good care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.11,0:19:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an important memory of your mother-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.97,0:19:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-san was taken in by the church\Nafter she lost her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.09,0:19:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First her father joined the army\Nand didn't come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And her mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.30,0:19:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her family lived on the Eastern\Nborder of Vingt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.96,0:19:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.94,0:19:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the town that was attacked\Nby the "Invisible Reaper."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when the two of them came to Seize,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,her mother had already taken\Nill, and shortly after...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:20:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that she was sorry she couldn't\Nbraid my hair anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so... And so she told me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to have it braided by the person\Nwho would care for me most.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Braid it for me, Yumina.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.52,0:20:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man lives on...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we part with those we love
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.60,0:20:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and suffer terribly because of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.07,0:20:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bravery is a very sad, very dear thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's already in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK! I'll join them soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.47,0:21:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.57,0:21:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I wanted to avoid washing my hair,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.07,0:21:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it didn't work out that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.81,0:21:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... Then... Then I'll dry it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted to touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you didn't buy the dolphin?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was your present to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.46,0:21:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio-sempai, do you believe in fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.91,0:21:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, something happened today\Nthat made me believe in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was enough of a reward for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate things that are decided or\Ngiven to you from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.19,0:22:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that something,\Nwhich someone did by mere coincidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.86,0:22:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,may go round and round, and eventually\Nchange someone's life in a big way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.49,0:22:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you call that fate, then maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.09,0:22:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.20,0:22:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you had a wonderful day, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.97,0:24:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Chirping Crickets - Spirits Down the River
